9f9e248260e554a20","tid":2353423,"uid":261268,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6b4e73f4ee4e9178c4d3c165c3e6fde7f7bb4d52","tid":2353423,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"我剩係想知你地幾不幸 咁我心理先會平衡返啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:42:32.000Z","msg":"乖 會遇到的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b178659b75b2d0e338c8d4a31152bf06ec581f55","tid":2353423,"uid":307282,"like":43,"dislike":5,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"基本上搵唔到我男朋友有咩缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n浪漫體貼溫柔醒目專一脾氣好有遠見孝順佢咩都齊哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從來都冇令我失望過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生日同聖誕用咗好多方法氹我開心<br />\n做嘢永遠都會考慮我感受<br />\n有時真係好驚會冇咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔敢想像有呢一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0ef8794a4e94d7ae36bf34915eac48ba546364","tid":2353423,"uid":113612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:35:05.000Z","msg":"我遇到個新嘅人 但佢好似唔太expressive"},{"pid":"024a611c96e90afd7178722b2360ea977f932423","tid":2353423,"uid":105366,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:39:25.000Z","msg":"冇嫌我窮。<br />\n富家女同屋企反面放棄遺產權都要跟著我捱。<br />\n又唔好名牌或珠寶。<br />\n啱啱十二月過左結婚二十週年。"},{"pid":"4b451cd721d244639f61384f42a3b63aa3447860","tid":2353423,"uid":197954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:45:27.000Z","msg":"真係好錫我 對我好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2307e293704d7479978e23cd9e458cc380f138","tid":2353423,"uid":207900,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:45:50.000Z","msg":"呢個topic開得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時感情台9成係出軌叫雞偷食性格不合，有時睇到對現實世界冇曬信心。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢個世界好大，有對既人有錯既人，focus喺自己想要既野上，始終會揾都啱你既另一半。"},{"pid":"34de6cb18dbac0450623fa9c8155923ce8124af1","tid":2353423,"uid":319469,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T20:05:40.000Z","msg":"好心軟 就算我做錯事激嬲佢 簡單講句sorry就會原諒我 唔會一直講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然講緊既係小事 大事就唔知因為未試過<br />\n<br />\n同埋好有交帶 每日佢去邊幾時出門口都會自動講 好有安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係一名毒撚宅男 無咩朋友 一年都唔會同朋友出到3次街 平時無野做就係屋企打機睇電視 雖然唔鍾意出街但係都好鍾意同我出街食下野行下 就算果日無見面我地都係keep住whatsapp 會打下電話 打下機咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好鍾意食野 同我一樣咁鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慢慢地鍾意食我鍾意食既野 我而加都鍾意食佢鍾意食既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada79a3fc98bb37ac188fd30fa2335dce136f78a","tid":2353423,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"024a611c96e90afd7178722b2360ea977f932423","tid":2353423,"uid":105366,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:39:25.000Z","msg":"冇嫌我窮。<br />\n富家女同屋企反面放棄遺產權都要跟著我捱。<br />\n又唔好名牌或珠寶。<br />\n啱啱十二月過左結婚二十週年。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:13:33.000Z","msg":"佢幾有錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5395f2297cea064f8a28bd8ae47af8f7de20cf24","tid":2353423,"uid":105366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ada79a3fc98bb37ac188fd30fa2335dce136f78a","tid":2353423,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"024a611c96e90afd7178722b2360ea977f932423","tid":2353423,"uid":105366,"like":62,"dislike":2,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:39:25.000Z","msg":"冇嫌我窮。<br />\n富家女同屋企反面放棄遺產權都要跟著我捱。<br />\n又唔好名牌或珠寶。<br />\n啱啱十二月過左結婚二十週年。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T00:13:33.